SMOKERS who quit now could save £400 in time for Christmas. Smokers who quit will be quids in SMOKERS who quit now could save £400 in time for Christmas.That's the message from smoking cessation practitioners at East Renfrewshire CHCP smokefree community services.The &pound;400 figure is based on the amount of money somone who smokes 20 cigarettes a day would spend between now and Christmas Day.Supports sessions are being held throughout the area. 